title: Keeper - Ratcheting Cargo Bar - Black/Silver, Adjustable From 40"-70"
description: Versatile: Expands from 40 in. to 70 in. length to fit most cars, trucks, and SUV’s; Please measure width of vehicle; Will expand to 70 inches. Ratchet to the ideal of length of your trunk, truck bed, etc. to hold in place on any terrain.
